text: Eremias fahimii (commonly known as Fahimi's racerunner) is a species of lizard in the family Lacertidae found in Iran. == Distribution and habitat == It is found in the Markazi Province up to the western side of Tehran Province. It may also occur in the Alborz, Qom, Qazvin and Zanjan provinces. == References == Category:Eremias
title: Eremias fahimii
